Package compiler.phase.seman

Class NameResolver

java.lang.Object
compiler.phase.seman.NameResolver
All Implemented Interfaces:
AST.FullVisitor<Object,NameResolver.Mode>, AST.Visitor<Object,NameResolver.Mode>
public class NameResolver extends Object implements AST.FullVisitor<Object,NameResolver.Mode>
Name resolver. The name resolver connects each node of a abstract syntax tree where a name is used with the node where it is defined. The only exceptions are struct and union component names which are connected with their definitions by the type resolver. The results of the name resolver are stored in SemAn.defAt.
